      <title>财政部的弗罗斯特表示，采取的措施将改善市场流动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/treasury-s-frost-says-key-steps-improve-market-liquidity-with-more-on-the-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部负责金融市场的助理部长乔舒亚·弗罗斯特 (Joshua Frost) 表示，全球最大债券市场的监管机构正在采取措施，确保美国国债交易更加安全、更具弹性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/treasury-s-frost-says-key-steps-improve-market-liquidity-with-more-on-the-way</guid>
