      <title>顶级预测者预测墨西哥比索将在选举抛售后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/usd-mxn-top-forecaster-sees-peso-rebound-after-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位顶级货币预测专家表示，墨西哥比索兑美元汇率可能在未来几个月内回升至 17，此前该国大选结果令人意外，导致比索在两天内下跌近 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/usd-mxn-top-forecaster-sees-peso-rebound-after-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 14:45:08 GMT</pubDate>
